        "href": "https://github.com/Jucian0/useform/issues"
      }}>{`issues page`}</a>{`. You can also take a look at the `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://github.com/Jucian0/useform/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md"
      }}>{`contributing guide`}</a>{`.`}</p>
